        "token": "313181878",
        "title": "Bourbon Friday // Networking & Bourbon Tasting",
        "description": "Join us at Techartista Central West End on Friday, April 17th, for Bourbon Friday, a weekly social gathering celebrating the St. Louis startup scene. Each week, we come together to share our stories, struggles, experiences, and, yes, a little bit of bourbon.\n\n**Mingle & Tastings // 4-7pm**\n\n**Parking & Transportation**\nStreet parking is available for Bourbon Friday.\nYou may also park in the church parking lot across the street from TechArtista.\nWe are also only a 1-mile Walk from [Central West End Metro Station](https://www.metrostlouis.org/metrolink-station/central-west-end-station/).\n\n**================================**\n\n**18+ to attend without a parent or legal guardian.**\n**21+ and up to drink ... obviously.**\n**Please Drink Responsibly.**\n\n*Underage drinking will result in removal from the event and a permanent ban from all future events.*",
